--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 2.0.0 (2019-01-24)
C: Rename option 'postgresql_monitor_mail_recipient' to 'postgresql_monitor_mail_from_address'
C: Rename option 'postgresql_monitor_mail_sender' to 'postgresql_monitor_mail_to_address'

* Version 0.2.8 (2019-01-22)
E: Improve script by throwing error message if script is executed interactively

* Version 0.2.7 (2019-01-21)
E: Improve script and reduce noise by removing echo command from alerting function

* Version 0.2.6 (2019-01-09)
E: Minor Shell script improvement to prevent globbing and word splitting

* Version 0.2.5 (2019-01-09)
E: Improve Shell script to prevent globbing and word splitting

* Version 0.2.4 (2018-12-13)
E: Minor style improvement

* Version 0.2.3 (2018-12-07)
E: Remove 'postgresql_monitor_mail_subject' parameter

* Version 0.2.2 (2018-12-07)
E: Remove email information from message

* Version 0.2.1 (2018-11-27)
E: Minor style improvements

* Version 0.2.0 (2018-10-29)
F: Add option to disable PostgreSQL backups (postgresql_run_backup_state)

* Version 0.1.0 (2018-10-08)
F: Initial release
